<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | Learnen</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/8182a1e71b.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/aboutUs_styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div id="header">
        <%- include('navbar'); %>
    </div>

    <div class="banner">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <p class="focus-in-expand-fwd">About Us</p>
        </div>
        <div class="caption-wrapper ">
            <p class="caption typewriter" id="caption">Learnen is a place for passionate teachers and curious students
                to share knowledge!</p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <section id="about">
        <div class="about-1">
            <h1>LEARNEN</h1>
            <p>
               With Learnen, skilled and experienced teachers can <b>make a learning room for students and post various assignments and resources</b> to aid their learning.

            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-2">
            <div class="content-box-lg">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="about-item text-center">
                                <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
                                <h3>MISSION</h3>
                                <hr>
                                <p>
                                    The mission of Learnen is to empower and inspire individuals to achieve their full potential through community-based learning. The platform aims to create a collaborative and supportive environment where passionate teachers and curious learners can come together to share knowledge, learn from each other, and grow together.                                    
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="about-item text-center">
                                <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
                                <h3>AIM</h3>
                                <hr>
                                <p>
                                    Learnen aims to create an engaging and interactive learning environment that encourages collaboration, creativity, and critical thinking. By connecting learners with passionate teachers and like-minded peers, Learnen aims to foster a sense of community and support that enhances the learning experience and helps individuals to achieve their full potential.
                                
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="about-item text-center">
                                <i class="fa fa-pencil"></i>
                                <h3>MOTTO</h3>
                                <hr>
                                <p>
                                     The motto of Learnen is "Where communities gather to grow together." This motto reflects the platform's focus on creating a collaborative and supportive environment where learners and teachers can come together to share knowledge, learn from each other, and achieve their goals.
                               
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div>
        <%- include('footer'); %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
